// Dimensions Collide: The Inter-Universal Impact
// Custom Title Screen Plugin for RPG Maker MV
// Based on the series by GalaxiaStar1128
//
// Features:
//   - Press Start screen with flashing text
//   - Freedom Planet 2 style main menu
//   - Hexagon icons per menu option
//   - Cyan & green color theme
//   - Start Game, Continue, Settings, Gallery, Time Attack, Quit
//   - NVDA / accessibility compatible (works with DimensionsCollide_Accessibility.js)
//
